Package: PopGenUtils
Type: Package
Title: A collection of useful functions to deal with genetic data in R
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Nikolaos Tourvas
Maintainer: Nikolaos Tourvas <nikostourvas@gmail.com>
Description: This package can be used to create a GenAlEx formatted file or a genind object from multiple GeneMapper txt files. It can also be used to calculate Probability of Identity (PID) & PIDsibs, which are useful statistics in forensic DNA analysis.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
